    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个教育场景下的OAuth 2.0授权流程图，核心是ClassroomService这个子系统。学生登录后访问成绩同步服务，然后获取令牌去请求课堂内容。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Login"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，我先确认一下结构。您提到学生登录，那起点应该是Education_StudentDB吗？还是需要一个独立的登录入口节点？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Login"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "起点就是StudentDB，学生数据存在那里。登录动作直接连到GradeSync服务，这是第一步。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Login"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我画好了：StudentDB通过Login指向GradeSync。接下来GradeSync要返回Access Token给StudentDB对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Access Token"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，拿到Access Token之后，StudentDB要带上Token去请求ClassroomService。这里标签写成\"Token + Request\"比较准确。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Access Token",
        "Token + Request"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加。那ClassroomService收到请求后需要验证权限，我画一个判断节点来检查scope，命名为Education_StudentDB？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Checks Scope"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，判断节点用菱形，但名字不对。检查scope的节点应该也叫Education_StudentDB吗？这容易和前面的数据节点混淆。不过按照我们的命名规范，确实都用StudentDB标识权限验证源。那就保持吧，但注意这是判断节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Checks Scope"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "了解，菱形判断节点，标签是Checks Scope。验证通过走Yes分支，不通过走No分支。通过的话返回什么？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Checks Scope",
        "Yes",
        "No"
